<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. سَأُرِيكَ بَعْضًا مِنْ مَعَائِبِ شُرْبِهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يَا صَاحِبي أَحْبَبَتْنِي أَمْ كَارِهِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>يُؤْذِي الكِرَامَ الكَاتِبِينَ بَنَتْنِهِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَأَمَاَم وَجْهِكَ شُعْلَةٌ مِنْ نَارِهِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>كَمْ مِنْ نُقُودٍ يَا فَتَى وَملابِسٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أَتْلَفْتَهَا بِشَرَائِهِ وَشَرَارِهِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَبِهِ الثَّاَنيَا اللؤْلُؤِيَّةِ أُفْسِدَتْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>بِقَبِيحِ لَوْنِ سَوَادِهِ وَصَفَارِهِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>كَانَتْ كَمِثْلِ الدُّرِ حُسْنًا شَانَهَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>مِنْ نَفْخِهَا الشِّدْقَيْنِ فِي مِزْمَارِهِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَتَرَا الصَّفَارَ عَلَى شَوَارِبِهِ بَدَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>مِنْ جَذْبِهِ الدُخَانَ مِنْ مِنْخَارِهِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَتَرَى الذِي فِي شُرْبِهِ مُتَوِلِهًا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>يَلْتَذُّ فِي الصُّهْرُوجِ بِاسْتِكْثَارِهِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَتَرَا الهَوَامَ إِذَا أَحَسَّ بِرِيحِهِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>تَرَكَ المَكَانَ وَفَرَّ مِنْ أَوْكَارِهِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَالنَّحْلُ لا تَلْوِي إليه لِخُبْثِهِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>أَبَدًا وَلا تَدْنُو إِلَى أَزْهَارِهِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَلِنَتْنِهِ وَلِقُبِحِهِ فِي طَعْمِهِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>لَمْ تَدْنُ سَائِمَةٌ إِلَى أَشْجَارِهِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>إِنْ خَالَطَ المَأْكُولُ مِنْهُ دُرَيْهِمٌ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>غَلَبَتْ خَبَائِثُه عَلَى قِنْطَارِهِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>